functions.name: Bork Credentials API
functions.purpose: Fetch Bork API credentials from unified api_credentials table
critical_findings: Must filter by provider='bork' to get Bork credentials

functions.name: Bork Process API
functions.purpose: Process raw Bork data in batches with fail-safe retry logic
critical_findings: Large batches cause database timeouts - process in batches of 10
Fail-safe retry logic with 3 attempts and 2-second delays
1-second delays between batches prevent database overload
Process ALL records (no LIMIT) with progress tracking
Progress logging shows batch completion percentage
Returns per-location processed counts for accurate UI display
Tracks processedByLocation object to match sync results confirmation context

functions.name: Bork Sync API
functions.purpose: Sync Bork API data for date ranges
critical_findings: Date format must be YYYYMMDD for Bork API
Timeout increased to 55s to prevent frontend timeout
Returns detailed feedback about API failures and record counts

functions.name: api-client
functions.purpose: Make Bork API calls with timeout protection
critical_findings: Returns empty array on API failure instead of throwing
Handles both connection timeouts and certificate errors

functions.name: cleanup-service
functions.purpose: Remove duplicate Bork sales data records, keeping only the most recent for each (location_id, date) pair

functions.name: RawDataStorage
functions.purpose: Display raw Bork API data from database
